            </b>From a <a href="highLunge.html">lunge</a> position with the left 
            foot forward, inhale and step forward into the left foot, straightening 
            the left leg. Straighten the right leg up parallel to the floor. </font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <!--2-->
          <td width="91%"><font size="2" face="Arial"><b><img src="images/2.GIF" width="18" height="18" align="MIDDLE" border="0" naturalsizeflag="3"> 
            </b>Staring at a point on the floor, place the left palm directly 
            under the left shoulder and carefully bring the right hand to the 
            right hip. Roll the right hip up and back so the hips face the side 
            wall </font></td>
        </tr>

        <tr> 
          <!--3-->
          <td width="91%"><font size="2" face="Arial"><b><img src="images/3.GIF" width="18" height="18" align="MIDDLE" border="0" naturalsizeflag="3"> 
            </b>Inhale the right fingertips up towards the ceiling. Turn the head 
            to face the side wall. Work on turning the whole torso to face the 
            side wall. </font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td width="91%"><font size="2" face="Arial"><img src="images/4.GIF" width="18" height="18" align="MIDDLE" border="0" naturalsizeflag="3"> 
