        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td width="91%"><font size="2" face="Arial"><img src="images/5.GIF" width="18" height="18" align="MIDDLE" border="0" naturalsizeflag="3"> 
            To release: exhale and slowly bring both hands back to the floor and 
            step the foot back into a <a href="highLunge.html">lunge</a>.</font></td>

        </tr>
